data.description: Amazing opportunity, just 45 minutes from North Bend. Live here year round or make it your weekend getaway. Double lot in the desirable community of Sunlight Waters. This stick-built home features radiant floor heating, amazing views and an almost 900 sq ft Shop. It has room for all of your toys and extra visitors with 4 220amp RV hook ups, two additional pads with septic dumps. This well built home has luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, 2 3/4 bathrooms open living room with great kitchen set up. Entertain or enjoy this beautiful setting all to yourself. The shop features a large bay door to store your RV, covered carport for additional parking and as much electrical as you could want. Great investment opportunity!
